result.title: 12th Iran Internet ACM ICPC Prep and Final — Asia 2014 Tehran
result.content:
Asia 2014 Tehran — Internet Programming Contest (2014) takes place on 27 Nov 2014. Registration starts on 21 Sep 2014 and ends on 26 Nov 2014. Contest is sponsored by University of Tehran. The above contest will be held on Sharecode and the contestant teams are consisted of 3 people. You should register for the contest on Baylor Site.

Happy Coding!
